About Me
My name is Noel Jung. I currently attend Queens
University in Kingston, Ontario. I enjoy swimming, playing video games
and fishing.
About the Project
Cool Games
I want to be able to create a website abotu the progression of the
scoreboards of some of my favourite video games.
Goals
Find a suitable game I want to cover
Might be hard to find a game that has a large number of players with
a scoreboard

Find a reliable scoreboard for the game
“This is data science”
~Preceptor
Kane’s Free High School
Data Science Bootcamp
